# arith-loop

Hot path: IntV boxing, env lookup, while-loop overhead.

```scalascript
def workload(): Long =
  var i = 0
  var sum = 0L
  while i < 1000000 do
    sum = sum + i
    i = i + 1
  sum

val WARMUP = 5
val REPS   = 20
var _w = 0
while _w < WARMUP do
  workload()
  _w += 1

val _t0 = System.currentTimeMillis()
var _r = 0
while _r < REPS do
  workload()
  _r += 1
val _ms = System.currentTimeMillis() - _t0
println(s"BENCH_MS: ${_ms.toDouble / REPS}")
```
